quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  26,111,"Ba re: “Re ka kholoa ho uena, empa batho ba eisehang ba u latetse morao?”"
  26,112,"A re: “Ke tseba joang ka tseo ba li etsang"
  26,113,"“Boikarabello ba bona bo ho Mong`a ka, hoja feela eba le utloisisa"
  26,114,“Ha ke’a tla ho tla phalalisa ba kholoang
  26,115,“Ke rometsoe ho hlokomelisa pepeneneng.”
  26,116,"Ba re: “Nooe, haeba u sa khaotse, u tla tlepetsoa ka majoe.”"
  26,117,"A re: “Mong`a ka! Ruri! Batho ba heso ba ea ntatola"
  26,118,"“Ak’u ahlole lipakeng tsa rona le bona ka kahlolo e senang leeme, U mpholose le ba kholoang bohle ba nang le ‘na.”"
  26,119,Eaba Re’a mo pholosa hammoho le bohle ba neng ba ena le eena ka Arekeng
  26,120,Kamor’a ho moo Ra khamisa bohle ba setseng ka metsi
  26,121,"Ruri ho sena ke sesupo, empa bongata ba bona ha bo kholoe"
  26,122,"Ruri! Mong’a hau, Ke Eena Ea Matla Oohle, U Tletse Mohau"
  26,123,Ba-Ad ba ile ba latola Baromuoa ba Allah
  26,124,"Ngoana bo bona Hud a re ho bona: “Na le sa tla ke le ts’abe Allah"
  26,125,“Ke moromuoa ea t`sepahalang ea romiloeng ho lona
  26,126,"“Kahoo, ts’abang Allah, le ‘mamele"
  26,127,“Ha ho moputso oo ke le kopang ona; moputso oa ka o ho Mong`a mafats’e feela
  26,128,“Na le ka aha sefika holim’a leralla le leng le le leng ho ithabisa
  26,129,"“Le aha le matlo a matle a bolulo, khopolong ea ho phela teng kahosafeleng"
  26,130,"“Ha le sebelisa matla a lona, le ea sebelisa joalo ka batho ba nang le matla oohle"
  26,131,"“Ts’abang Allah, le ‘mamele"
  26,132,“Ts’abang Eena Ea le sitsitseng ka lintho tsohle tseo le li tsebang
  26,133,“U le setsitse ka makhomo le bara
  26,134,“Lirapa le liliba tse ts’akhunyang
  26,135,“Ke na le ts’abo ea Kahlolo ea mohla Letsatsi le Ts’abehang.”
  26,136,"Ba re: “Ho ea ts’oana ho rona hore na u oa re khalema kapa u ba sieo hara bakhalemi"
  26,137,"“Tsena ha se letho, haese tsona linthoana tsa mehleng ea khale"
  26,138,«Ha re ke ba ka amohelang mahloko kapa likahlolo!»
  26,139,"Ba ile ba mo latola; Ra ba ripitla. Ruri! ho sena ke sesupo, empa boholo ba bona bo sa kholoe"
  26,140,"Ruri! Mong’a hau U Matla Oohle, Mohau Oa Hae o’a Khaphatseha"
  26,141,"Ba-Thamud, ba ile ba latola Baromuoa ba Allah"
  26,142,"Ngoana bo bona Salih a re ho bona: “Na le sa tla ke le Ts’abe"
  26,143,“Ke moromuoa ea t`sepahalang ea romiloeng ho lona
  26,144,"“Kahoo, ts’abang Allah, le ‘mamele"
  26,145,“Ha ho moputso oo ke le kopang oona; moputso oa ka o ho Mong`a mafats’e feela
  26,146,“Na le hopola hore le ts’ireletsong ka lintho tsohle tseo le nang le tsona hajoale
  26,147,“Lirapa le liliba tse ts’akhunyang
  26,148,“Masimo a poone le lifate tsa lipalema tse behileng haholo hooli ka ‘nang tsa robeha
  26,149,“Le hona ho honya mafika ho etsa matlo ka botsebi bo matla
  26,150,“Empa ts’abang Allah le ‘mamele
  26,151,“Le se latele taelo ea ea lehlasoa
  26,152,"“Ea jalang pherekano lefats’eng, ea sa rateng ho sokoloha.”"
  26,153,"Ba re: “uena u e mong oa ba louoeng"
  26,154,"“U motho joalo ka rona. Kahoo, hlahisa sesupo haeba u bua `nete.”"
  26,155,"Salih a re: “Bonang, kamele ke ena e ts’ehali. Le eona e na le tokelo ea ho noa Selibeng ka letsatsi le leng, le lona le na le tokelo e joalo ka letsatsi le leng, empa ka letsatsi le boletsoeng"
  26,156,«Le se e nt`se kotsi esere la tloha la oeloa ke Kahlolo ea Letsatsi le Ts’abehang.”
  26,157,"Empa ba ile bae khakhatha, eaba ba apareloa ke masoabi"
  26,158,"Ba oeloa ke kahlolo. Ruri! ho sena ke sesupo, empa bongata ba bona bo sa kholoe"
  26,159,"Ruri! Mong’a hau U Matla Oohle, U Tletse Mohau"
  26,160,Batho ba habo Lota ba ile ba latola Baromuoa ba Allah
  26,161,"Ngoana’bo bona Lota a re ho bona: “Na le sa tla ke le Ts’abe"
  26,162,‹Ke moromuoa ea t`sepahalang ea romiloeng ho lona
  26,163,"“Kahoo, ts’abang Allah le ‘mamele"
  26,164,“Ha ho moputso oo ke le kopang ho lona; moputso oa ka o ho Mong`a mafats’e feela
  26,165,“Har’a libopuoa tsohle lefats’eng le arorelana likobo le banna ba bang
  26,166,"“Le siee bao Mong`a lona a le hloletseng bona? Che, le batho ba tlotseng meeli eohle.”"
  26,167,"Ba re: “Oho Lota haeba u sa khaotse, ruri u tla lelekoa.”"
  26,168,"A re: “Ke hloile liketso tsa lona"
  26,169,“Mong`a ka! Ak’u mpholose le ba lelapa la ka ho tseo ba li etsang!”
  26,170,"Re ile ra mo pholosa ‘moho lebalelapa la hae,-bohle"
  26,171,“Ntle feela le mosali moholo ea neng a le har’a ba neng ba salatse morao
  26,172,Empa Ra ripitla bohle
  26,173,"Ra ba nesetsa majoe a lengetana: E ts’abehang pula ho ba neng ba khaleng’oe"
  26,174,"Ruri! ho sena ke sesupo, empa bongata ba bona bo sa kholoe"
  26,175,"Ruri! Mong’a hau U Matla Oohle, U Tletse Mohau"
  26,176,Balekane ba Moru ba ile ba latola Baromuoa ba Allah
  26,177,"Shuaib a re ho bona: “Na le sa tla ke le Ts’abe"
  26,178,“Ke moromuoa ea ts’epahalang ea romiloeng ho lona
  26,179,“Kahoo ts’abang Allah le ‘mamele
  26,180,“Ha ho moputso oo ke le kopang ona; moputso oa ka o tsoa ho Mong`a mafats’e feela